issue.body:
in file <code>layout/base.j2</code>, I have a block in head tag

<pre>
  {% block syntaxhighlighter_css %}
  {% endblock syntaxhighlighter_css %}
</pre>


in file <code>content/blog/post-name.html</code>

overriding the block with following content,

<pre>
<code>
{% block syntaxhighlighter_css %}
&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ media_url('css/shCore.css') }}" type="text/css" /&gt;
&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ media_url('css/shThemeDefault.css') }}" type="text/css" /&gt;
{% endblock syntaxhighlighter_css %}
</code>
</pre>


after generating with <code>hyde gen</code>, in the file <code>deploy/blog/post-name.html</code>
the link tags are duplicated in both <code>head</code> tag as-well-as in <code>body</code> tag.

